## Quick Reference

**The ONE Command:**
```bash
anox smartfix --vibe=focus    # Fix bugs NOW
```

**Vibes:**
```bash
anox smartfix --vibe=chill    # ğŸŒŠ Ultra-safe (max 1 file)
anox smartfix --vibe=focus    # ğŸ¯ Balanced (max 3 files)
anox smartfix --vibe=hacker   # âš¡ Aggressive (max 10 files)
anox smartfix --vibe=explain  # ğŸ“š Read-only (0 files)
```

**Mobile:**
```bash
anox sync                     # Offline-first sync
anox mobile                   # Mobile API server
```

**Help:**
```bash
anox --help                   # Full command list
anox smartfix --help          # Smartfix options
```

